Arduino libraries for vts8787 (Pixetto)

Copyright (C) 2019  VIA Technologies, Inc. All rights reserved.

Changelog

2020-01-02  Release v3.0.1
 * Integrate SmartSensor classes for SoftwareSerial and HardwareSerial into one class.
 
2019-12-11  Release v3.0.0 (for Pixetto only)
 * Only keep libraries for Smart Sensor. Remove all other libraries.

2019-12-04  Release v2.0.0
 * Add SmartSensor and SmartSensor-hwserial functions.
 * Fix AutoCar bugs:
	 - Add moto protection
	 - Remove calibration of turn angle

2019-03-12  Release v1.2.2 (supported vts8654x version v1.7.1)
 * AutoCar API refactoring
 * Remove useless variables

2019-03-12  Release v1.2.1 (supported version v1.7.1)
 * Fix note detection doesn't work

2019-03-08  Release v1.2.0 
 * Add enable/disable feature of driveless car
 * Config motor and servo API refactoring

2019-02-26  Release v1.1 (supported version v1.7.0)
 * Add arduino LED control function

2019-01-17  Release v1.0
 * Works on Firmware version v1.6.20 ~ v1.7.0
